  <brief_title>Cognitive-Behavioral Therapy for Adults With Attention-Deficit/Hyperactivity Disorder Inattentive Presentation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Group-Based Cognitive-Behavioral Therapy for Adults With Attention-Deficit/Hyperactivity Disorder Inattentive Presentation: Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
